 ```JavaScript
   fooExecutionContext = {
      variableObject: {
          arguments: {
              0: 22,
              length: 1
          },
          i: 22,
          c: pointer to function c()
          a: undefined,
          b: undefined
      },
      scopeChain: { ... },
      this: { ... }
    }
  ```
